956
01:32:01,700 --> 01:32:03,700
It is so much nicer in Nice

957
01:32:45,900 --> 01:32:46,995
And now I really must go.

958
01:32:47,529 --> 01:32:49,931
Polly, would you kiss me goodbye?

959
01:32:50,500 --> 01:32:51,800
Yes, if you want me to.

960
01:32:54,700 --> 01:32:55,700
Is that all right?

961
01:32:56,070 --> 01:32:59,607
Yes, we are perfect.
