962
01:33:00,300 --> 01:33:03,600
If I just get through the show
it'd be enough for me.

963
01:33:04,679 --> 01:33:06,581
It was nice of you
to rehearse with me, Alf. Thanks.

964
01:33:07,215 --> 01:33:09,417
That's alright.
I wish I was playing Tony.

965
01:33:12,220 --> 01:33:13,555
I'm glad I couldn't find him.

966
01:33:14,822 --> 01:33:16,257
