967
01:33:17,692 --> 01:33:18,760
Yet he is very kind.

968
01:33:20,562 --> 01:33:21,996
I suppose I'm just not his type.

969
01:33:23,998 --> 01:33:25,867
I wonder who he'd really go for.

970
