978
01:34:21,100 --> 01:34:24,900
Percy, Percy,
please, have mercy

979
01:34:25,000 --> 01:34:28,496
Why must you always
be so sad and gloomy?

980
01:34:29,464 --> 01:34:32,700
Why can't you be
a little nicer to me?

981
01:34:33,100 --> 01:34:36,900
