I've got those dreary

1002
01:35:47,300 --> 01:35:48,700
weary

1003
01:35:48,900 --> 01:35:51,879
You-don't-want-to-play-with-me blues

1004
01:36:56,600 --> 01:36:58,760
She told me she had a headache
