1027
01:38:19,800 --> 01:38:22,830
But Maisie, when are you
going to come and see my yacht again?

1028
01:38:23,798 --> 01:38:25,132
You liked that, didn't you?

1029
01:38:25,132 --> 01:38:27,702
Yes, it's a very dinky yacht.

1030
01:38:28,703 --> 01:38:30,071
I like yachts.

1031
01:38:31,072 --> 01:38:32,039
Mademoiselle Maisie.

1032
01:38:33,400 --> 01:38:34,600
Alphonse.

1033
01:38:35,900 --> 01:38:37,545
You look "ravissant".

1034
01:38:38,079 --> 01:38:39,580
Behave yourself or
I'll belt you.

1035
01:38:39,580 --> 01:38:41,182
Just try it,
you little twerp.

1036
01:38:42,383 --> 01:38:44,886
Do not forget tonight
she will dance the tango with me.

1037
01:38:44,886 --> 01:38:46,521
Of course not.

1038
01:38:47,400 --> 01:38:49,860
-Maisie!
-Michael!

1039
01:38:49,900 --> 01:38:52,800
You look enchanting.
Tonight you and I will dance the two-step.

1040
01:38:52,900 --> 01:38:55,700
I can hardly wait.

1041
01:38:56,564 --> 01:38:57,765
Pack it in,
you old cow.

1042
01:38:57,765 --> 01:38:59,834
Droop off,
you faded pansy.

1043
01:39:02,100 --> 01:39:03,760
I too want to dance
with you at the ball.

1044
01:39:03,800 --> 01:39:04,960
You beat-up old bag.

1045
01:39:05,000 --> 01:39:08,000
